Stewart is an unincorporated community in Lake County, Minnesota, United States. It is a surrounding community of Two Harbors.
The community is located seven miles north of the city of Two Harbors at the intersection of Lake County Roads 124 and 132.
Lake County Roads 12 and 111 are also in the immediate area. Stewart is located within Lake No. 2 Unorganized Territory of Lake County. The Stewart River flows through the community. The Two Harborsâ€“Richard B. Helgeson Airport is nearby.
Stewart is located within ZIP code 55616 based in Two Harbors.
